headline: Quanta Services (NYSE:PWR) Declares US$0.10 Quarterly Dividend to Shareholders
summary: Quanta Services (NYSE:PWR) affirmed its quarterly dividend, boosting investor confidence as its share price increased by approximately 26% over the last month. This price move correlates with several significant developments, including the announcement of a lucrative $1.7 billion contract for the Grain Belt Express project, enhanced earnings figures, and raised corporate guidance.
